#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.softmax.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.softmax"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:1 of
msgid ""
"Compute the softmax function. The softmax function transforms each "
"element of a collection by computing the exponential of each element "
"divided by the sum of the exponentials of all the elements. That is, if "
"`x` is a one-dimensional numpy array::"
msgstr ""
"计算 softmax 函数。softmax 函数通过计算每个元素的指数除以所有元素指数之和"
"来变换集合中的每个元素。也就是说，如果 `x` 是一个一维 numpy 数组::"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:9 of
msgid "Input array."
msgstr "输入数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:11 of
msgid ""
"Axis to compute values along. Default is None and softmax will be "
"computed over the entire array `x`."
msgstr "计算值所沿的轴。默认为 None，此时将在整个数组 `x` 上计算 softmax。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:15 of
msgid ""
"**s** -- An array the same shape as `x`. The result will sum to 1 along "
"the specified axis."
msgstr "**s** -- 与 `x` 形状相同的数组。结果在指定轴上的总和为 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:20 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:21 of
msgid ""
"The formula for the softmax function :math:`\\sigma(x)` for a vector "
":math:`x = \\{x_0, x_1, ..., x_{n-1}\\}` is"
msgstr ""
"向量 :math:`x = \\{x_0, x_1, ..., x_{n-1}\\}` 的 softmax 函数 :math:`\\"
"sigma(x)` 的公式为"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:24 of
msgid ""
"\\sigma(x)_j = \\frac{e^{x_j}}{\\sum_k e^{x_k}}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:26 of
msgid "The `softmax` function is the gradient of `logsumexp`."
msgstr "`softmax` 函数是 `logsumexp` 的梯度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:28 of
msgid ""
"The implementation uses shifting to avoid overflow. See [1]_ for more "
"details."
msgstr "该实现使用偏移来避免溢出。详见 [1]_。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:32 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:33 of
msgid ""
"P. Blanchard, D.J. Higham, N.J. Higham, \"Accurately computing the log-"
"sum-exp and softmax functions\", IMA Journal of Numerical Analysis, "
"Vol.41(4), :doi:`10.1093/imanum/draa038`."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:38 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:47 of
msgid "Compute the softmax transformation over the entire array."
msgstr "在整个数组上计算 softmax 变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:58 of
msgid ""
"Compute the softmax transformation along the first axis (i.e., the "
"columns)."
msgstr "沿第一个轴（即列）计算 softmax 变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.misc.softmax:69 of
msgid "Compute the softmax transformation along the second axis (i.e., the rows)."
msgstr "沿第二个轴（即行）计算 softmax 变换。"

